into that room.

136
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:11,639
Right!

137
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:12,200
Exactly!

138
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:14,759
I left the dance hall
at the Shen hour today

139
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,240
