141
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,000
She couldn't be here.

142
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,720
You're all in this together.

143
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:22,360
Of course you'd defend her!

144
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,080
Hey!

145
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,200
Make way! Make way!

146
00:09:26,624 --> 00:09:27,519
Jiang Xueying,

147
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:29,159
