148
00:09:29,159 --> 00:09:30,600
Come with us to the yamen.

149
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,919
Who dares!

150
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:34,016
Does being Princess Consort
exempt you from the law

151
00:09:34,016 --> 00:09:35,759
and disregard human life?

152
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:36,600
- Right!
- Exactly!

153
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,919
Are our lives not lives too?

154
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:39,639
Law makes

155
00:09:39,639 --> 00:09:40,399
no exception.

156
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:41,000
How could you?

157
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:41,679
It's outrageous.

158
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,879
Please prioritize the greater good.

159
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,400
The law must be enforced.

160
00:09:47,392 --> 00:09:48,360
I'll go with you.

161
00:09:49,632 --> 00:09:50,200
Xueying.

162
00:09:51,168 --> 00:09:52,279
This matter is suspicious.

163
00:09:52,768 --> 00:09:54,399
Someone must have impersonated me

164
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,360
and framed me.

165
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:57,360
My words hold no defense.

166
00:09:57,679 --> 00:09:59,440
Only you can find evidence for me

167
00:09:59,639 --> 00:10:00,399
and clear my name.

168
00:10:05,024 --> 00:10:05,960
Don't worry.

169
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:07,120
I will rescue you.

170
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,960
Sir, have you seen
the woman in the portrait?

171
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:07,360
Ah, it's her.

172
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:09,039
Last night this gentleman

173
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:11,136
