176
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,559
She wasn't at Jingwu Hall.

177
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:17,000
Now release her.

178
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:19,360
Only Your Highness
and the shop owner can testify

179
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,240
