189
00:11:39,679 --> 00:11:40,600
Are you sure?

190
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,039
Was it someone resembling her?

191
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:42,759
I swear!

192
00:11:42,759 --> 00:11:44,800
That girl resisted and ran out at first.

193
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:46,464
The Princess Consort
escorted her back in.

194
00:11:46,464 --> 00:11:47,639
