196
00:11:48,559 --> 00:11:49,720
She got drunk so fast?

197
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:50,944
I don't know!

198
00:11:59,559 --> 00:12:01,639
According to the dance hall witnesses,

199
00:12:02,336 --> 00:12:05,720
'I' arrived there during the You hour

200
00:12:06,159 --> 00:12:09,440
