after entering the main hall.

201
00:12:12,704 --> 00:12:14,000
(She knew my movements,)

202
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:15,960
(knowing I wasn't there,)

203
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:18,240
(so she dared to impersonate me.)

204
00:12:19,159 --> 00:12:20,039
(Then)

205
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,200
('I' encountered Musician Yang)

206
00:12:22,919 --> 00:12:24,240
(and comforted her briefly)

207
00:12:24,448 --> 00:12:26,360
(before helping her re-enter the room.)

208
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,519
(If she was unwilling,)

209
00:12:28,896 --> 00:12:30,840
