248
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:36,879
My son...

249
00:15:40,759 --> 00:15:42,200
She told me to strangle

250
00:15:42,919 --> 00:15:44,480
Jiang Xueying and stage it as suicide.

251
00:15:45,344 --> 00:15:46,320
